snippet.title: Rexaura Trailer
snippet.description:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/317790

Rexaura is a mod for Portal 1 based on high energy pellets and several new mechanics surrounding them.

Features:
- A campaign with 20 test chambers
- Bonus and advanced chambers
- Dialogue
- Music
